{"tid":2186446,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"欣賞漢字漢文漢典，日本人也是有自己歷史的。百粵人、香港人也有","createTime":"2020-09-03T03:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T04:34:30.000Z","uid":261647,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"36699d1ec9656adbd47821858da8ec28b1d14d62","tid":2186446,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T03:38:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1298818275812335616\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1298818275812335616&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hQb0NiVgWGuYP6yHf6H5SmE%3D&h=96143e20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1298818275812335616&h=76efc136\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1298818275812335616</a><br />\n<br />\n正如日本人欣賞漢字、漢文、漢典，但也是有自己歷史的。我們的文明本來就很不同。他們是城池文明。台灣是大肚王國、賽德克巴萊。百粵地帶是商貿之地，早就有強國貿易制裁鄰國，漢唐或後他們記載，這邊充滿瘴氣，視這裡的人如同山精妖怪。蜑家是水上民族。陸上則是土樓文明、圍村文明，村落戰爭發達。"},{"pid":"ac5a870ad861aaa38a50bab6c9bc7d7ca9225448","tid":2186446,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T03:42:49.000Z","msg":"漢人點睇我地<br />\n<br />\n表接壤荊楚溪峒聚落悉為南蠻其種非一曰猺曰獞曰獠曰狼曰狑曰犽曰㺜曰狪曰𤝣曰猀曰狸曰蜑皆性習獷野罔知禮教"},{"pid":"79614ee9978ab0224721067da3b6d3673570d150","tid":2186446,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T03:43:27.000Z","msg":"閩，蜑<br />\n全部有貶義"},{"pid":"9a46d282d33c7149565488e55278f5b7d3363347","tid":2186446,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T03:45:18.000Z","msg":"中史其實就係垃圾洗我地腦<br />\n嚴重扭曲歷史<br />\n應該學百越史及東亞史<br />\n香港史"},{"pid":"baa44c4dbb27b9f01ea3e9206307f668d5e80d4b","tid":2186446,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T03:45:51.000Z","msg":"咁個作者由一開始唔應該用中文而係用粵文啦"},{"pid":"88f5116c44cca08f494700e785acf788e7de153b","tid":2186446,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"baa44c4dbb27b9f01ea3e9206307f668d5e80d4b","tid":2186446,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T03:45:51.000Z","msg":"咁個作者由一開始唔應該用中文而係用粵文啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T03:47:42.000Z","msg":"香港本土史，分為百越派同漢派"},{"pid":"9743075080bf9a4dd0101a352d962950732c67f0","tid":2186446,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:07:34.000Z","msg":"到底喺廣東人歷史定喺香港人歴史？？<br />\n而且廣東人喺混血民族<br />\n百越人同北方漢人已經撈埋一齊<br />\n咁樣廣東人仲喺咪百越人？？"},{"pid":"6757933371058ad661aa175a5b2b28583faaeb72","tid":2186446,"uid":66242,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2bd2e7daf3d41ac0dac5246e830093130c80dfd","tid":2186446,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"79614ee9978ab0224721067da3b6d3673570d150","tid":2186446,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T03:43:27.000Z","msg":"閩，蜑<br />\n全部有貶義"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:31:02.000Z","msg":"不如好似和字 /  喃字咁<br />\n<br />\n直接創製粵字<br />\n<br />\n刪除 / 改走虫部 is OK"},{"pid":"3d13405dc61222c10bddb1bab4a6036e6d2a26c9","tid":2186446,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9a46d282d33c7149565488e55278f5b7d3363347","tid":2186446,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T03:45:18.000Z","msg":"中史其實就係垃圾洗我地腦<br />\n嚴重扭曲歷史<br />\n應該學百越史及東亞史<br />\n香港史"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:34:30.000Z","msg":"應該編修:<br />\n(1)《百越史》 (史前至1842年); 及<br />\n(2) 《香港史》(1842年至今)"}]}